These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
City: san-francisco, hannover, new-york, rome
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of City:new-york##1
2. City:rome is on the far left##1
3. City:new-york is between City:hannover and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| City      | rome | san-francisco | new-york   | hannover |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Music-Genre: folk, r&b, dubstep, salsa
1. Music-Genre:salsa is between Hobby:reading and Music-Genre:r&b##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Music-Genre:dubstep is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Music-Genre:folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | salsa   | folk | dubstep       |

