.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
Sport: sailing, lacrosse, ice-hockey, volleyball
1. Sport:ice-hockey is on the right of Food:kale##1
2. Sport:ice-hockey is between Sport:lacrosse and Food:corn##2
3. Sport:lacrosse is on the far left##1
4. Sport:volleyball is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == Sport:volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Sport   | lacrosse | ice-hockey   | volleyball | sailing |

